BETA-CRITICAL FEATURES:
- Insert a new trip into the database
- Display trip details
	-name, address, organizer's phone, date and time
- Add a person into the trip
	-Name, preffered departure time, takes car - yes, if necessary, no
- Add car details
	-color, capacity, meeting point
- Automatically distribute people into cars
	-First fill up "yes" cars, then if necessary: 1st by capacity, 2nd by departure time
	-Each going car should have the same number of empty seats

